nl.renarj.jasdb.api

Class SimpleEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.renarj.jasdb.api.SimpleEntity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, CachableItem, IndexableItem
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EmbeddedEntity

    public class SimpleEntity
extends Object
implements Serializable, CachableItem, IndexableItem
    This is the public API storage entity, this is stored in the DB and all indexes are updated based on the index definitions. The Entity allows adding of properties and nested entities which will automatically be serialized into the internal storage format.
    Author:
    Renze de Vries
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
